==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Autograph
<hw>Au"to*graph</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>autographe</ets>, fr. Gr. <?/ autographic; <?/ self + <?/ to
write.]</ety> <def>That which is written with one's own hand; an
original manuscript; a person's own signature or handwriting.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Autograph</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Autograph
<hw>Au"to*graph</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>In one's own
handwriting; <as>as, an <ex>autograph</ex> letter; an <ex>autograph</ex>
will.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Autographal</ent>⟦br⟧
